Sidney Ainsworth https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sidney_Ainsworth 0 Sidney Ainsworth (December 21, 1872 – May 21, 1922) was a screen and stage actor who appeared in his first movie in 1909. He was born in Manchester, England and died in Madison, Wisconsin, United States.
